author: The Current
description: The title track from @polica's new LP "Dreams Go" became a live-show fan favorite over the last decade, originally intended for the Minneapolis electronica band's 2016 record "United Crushers." The vocals were re-recorded at Pachyderm Studios in 2023, homing in the emotional counterbalance of angst and buoyancy. Hear it Sunday nights on The Local Show. Hit Play!
title: Poliça's Channy Leaneagh talks about "Dreams Go" #poliça

author: The Current
description:
To celebrate The Current’s 20th Anniversary, The Current’s Live Sessions Vault unlocks never-before-seen live performance videos of bands and artists who have played in our iconic studio. 

Watch to see the full session and interview of Dum Dum Girls featuring previously unreleased footage, from when they visited The Current studio back in 2014.

00:02:47 In The Wake Of You
00:05:15 Coming Down
